cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO 

This paper proposes a new cost volume formulation for multi-view stereo and stereo matching that is memory and time efficient. The paper focuses on computer vision and graphics, which suggests that cs.CV and cs.GR are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that cs.LG and cs.AI are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves robotics applications, which suggests that cs.RO is a possible sub-category as well.
